that some goods are damaged. A must inform P and get instructions in this
regard.
5. Duty on Termination of Agency
When an agency terminates due to the death or insanity of principal, the
agent must take reasonable steps for the protection of interests of the legal
representatives of late principal. (Sec. 209)
