He has a right to retain the goods and refuse delivery thereof until his
charges of hire are paid. If no charges are paid he can exercise particular lien
over the goods. The lien cannot be enforced if the carrier has agreed to give
credit.
3. Sue others
The carrier has a special right regarding the goods delivered to him for
