secured, award or settlement secured by workman under any other law.
2. To represent any workman in any proceedings.
3. To give notice of and declare a strike under the rules.
4. To nominate workmen on the Boards of Trustees of any welfare institutions,
Provident Funds and Workers Participation Fund.
5. To nominate Shop Steward to create a link between the workers and
employers.
6. To nominate representatives of the management committee.
7. To appoint auditors to audit the accounts of the company from workers point
of view.
